Summary: We never saw it until we looked at the picture.
divs: sighting detailswe were standing on our back deck facing west & taking pictures of the sky,we didn't notice the object until we looked at the pictures & decided to send it to you for your opinion.approximatly 2 weeks before this around 1 in the afternoon i saw 2 silver objects darting above the house-along ways in the sky,they looked like small dots, but were moving up,down & darting back & forth for 2-3 minutes before they disappeared,i told my wife when she got home that i had saw a ufo & now this picture... she's starting to believe too.anyway,take a look please & let me know what you think,you'll see a vertical cigar shaped object(reflection?)in the middle of the picture. thanks,*(name deleted--sgonzalez\cms).
